1
00:00:00,508 --> 00:00:02,408
应当处死!
He deserves to die!

2
00:00:02,410 --> 00:00:04,277
这个人和"神的儿子"是一伙的!
This man walks with this "Son of God"!

3
00:00:04,279 --> 00:00:07,546
我不是! 我不认识他!
I do not! I don't know him!

4
00:00:07,548 --> 00:00:09,749
啊!
Aah!

5
00:00:09,751 --> 00:00:12,985
我愿贡献出我自己的墓地 作为您儿子的安息之地
I would like to offer my own tomb as your son's final place of rest.

6
00:00:12,987 --> 00:00:15,087
他被处决是因为反复亵渎神明
He was killed for the repeated blasphemy

7
00:00:15,089 --> 00:00:16,655
声称自己是弥赛亚
of claiming to be the Messiah.

8
00:00:16,657 --> 00:00:17,723
如果他是呢?
And if he was?

9
00:00:17,725 --> 00:00:20,626
一旦他们认识到你们的启示仍是威胁
Once the Romans realize your message remains a threat,

10
00:00:20,628 --> 00:00:22,261
他们会将你们连根拔除
they will root you out.

11
00:00:22,263 --> 00:00:25,798
那个拿撒勒人也不过是血肉之躯
The Nazarene was only ever flesh and blood.

12
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,302
我要你在亚利马太的坟墓布下寺庙的守卫
I want you to post temple guards at Arimathea's tomb.

13
00:00:29,304 --> 00:00:30,937
必须封死墓穴
It must remain sealed.

14
00:00:30,939 --> 00:00:35,675
在第三日 他保证会起死回生
On the third day, he promises to rise from death.

15
00:00:35,677 --> 00:00:39,278
我会在墓穴外安排一个小的守卫队
I will post a small guard outside the tomb.

16
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:41,447
封条已经被破坏了
The Roman seal has been broken.

17
00:00:41,449 --> 00:00:44,183
坟墓已经打开了 那个拿撒勒人... 不见了
The tomb is now open, and the Nazarene... is gone.

18
00:00:44,185 --> 00:00:46,352
"不见了"是什么意思?
What do you mean, "gone"?

